Package: lightgraph
Type: Package
Title: High-Performance HTML Canvas-Based Network Visualization
Version: 1.2.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Hao", "Zhu", email = "haozhu233@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Donna", "Slonim", email = "donna.slonim@tufts.edu", role = "aut")
    )
Description: A lightweight R binding for the 'lightGraph' JavaScript library,
    which renders interactive network visualizations on HTML canvas for
    high performance. Provides an 'htmlwidgets' interface with weighted
    edges, groups and community detection, metric-driven node styling, and
    built-in graph analytics (degree, betweenness, closeness, eigenvector,
    PageRank, components, and communities).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    htmlwidgets (>= 1.5.0)
Suggests:
    igraph,
    jsonlite,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
